    "It provides a set of modules for generating sentences from structured data, making it suitable for converting triples into abstractive sentences.",
    "The selection of triples from the KG for abstract generation is determined by the compression rate.",
    "Given that the DUC-2002 dataset comprises human-generated abstracts with word limits of 50, 100, and 200 words, we consider these specific word limits as the compression rates.",
